{
  "texts": [
    "Having a gold standard of human evaluation with lesser standards for evaluation using LLMs seems to be a possible way forward.",
    "As in other areas where LLMs are highly performant such as code generation, we should start to accustom ourself to a world where clinicians supervise AI systems that reason independently.",
    "In the future the job of the clinician might be to supervise an AI system that independently gives suggestions for diagnosis and treatment.",
